At simpleERB we are committed to safeguarding and preserving the privacy of our users. This Privacy and Cookie Policy (together with our terms and conditions) explains what happens to any personal data simpleERB collects from you or that you share with the simpleERB, e.g. the simpleERB website or data that we collect from you whilst you use simpleERB.
