Emails
When we send you emails we may include "single pixel images" to help us to track information like when you opened the email, (or didn’t open it all.) You can change your email client settings so that we can’t do this
In addition to marketing messages that you opt into we may send you messages about technical issues, e.g. planned outages, releases and changes to this policy or our terms of use, customer support, to meet legal requirements, to communicate with you about your account.
Unsubscribe:
We will NOT send you marketing emails or texts directly, only "transactional" ones e.g about a reservation. If you receive marketing communications from a "simpleERB restaurant" it will NOT be from us. The restaurant is not allowed to use the simpleERB SMS messaging service to send you marketing communications (however this use is unlikely as they cannot do this in bulk form).
